name: v0.8.5
body: Upgraded some deps, added table drawer (overflow on same page)

name: v0.8.4
body: Added column settings #126

name: v0.8.3
body: Updated libraries, fixed alignment in vertical cells, updated README

name: v0.8.2
body: Fix for #110 and introducing #114

name: v0.8.1
body: Fix for issue #106

name: v0.8.0
body: The settings object is now hidden and not publicly exposed anymore, some properties have higher visibility for more flexible subclassing and versions have been adapted.

name: v0.7.1
body: Added config option in `TableDrawer` for compression in content stream.

name: v0.7.0
body: Border styles and fix for issue #89

name: v0.6.6
body: Fixes #86

name: v0.6.5
body: Small fix for #85, very minor changes

name: v0.6.4
body: Corrected a missing `<scope>test</scope>` in the `pom.xml` file

name: v0.6.3
body: Fixing an issue with row spanning and auto-sizing height (#74), improving line breaking (#79, #81) and introducing automatic comparison of PDF files for integration tests

name: v0.6.2
body: Introduced configuration for number of rows to repeat on `RepeatedHeaderTableDrawer`, fixed #62

name: v0.6.1
body: Introduced `getFinalY()` method in `TableDrawer`, fixed image scaling bug (https://github.com/vandeseer/easytable/issues/64)

name: v0.6.0
body: Mainly introduced `ParagraphCell`, also did some refactorings

name: v0.5.2
body: Performance improvements, bugfix for row spanning related issue

name: v0.5.1
body: Added possibility to draw several multipage tables on a document (https://github.com/vandeseer/easytable/issues/45), minor improvements on text splitting

name: v0.5.0
body: Refactorings, allow for custom table/cell drawers

name: v0.4.3
body: Introduced a `TableDrawer` that can repeat the header on every new page and fixed issue with image sizing on row spanning.

name: v0.4.2
body: Make the `TableDrawer` adjustable, fix image centering

name: v0.4.1
body: Solves #32

name: v0.4.0
body: Introduced row spanning

name: v0.3.0
body: Fixed some bugs, added more styling possibilities and made the lib available to maven central.

name: v0.1.0
body: More consistent API (usage of Lombok builders), word breaking, line spacing, vertical alignment

name: v0.0.13
body: Text wrapping
Fixed issue with column span width
Adds setting different fonts per cell and row spanning
